{"bodyHtml": "<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"></head>\n<body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f0f0f0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\">\n<div style=\"display:none;font-size:1px;color:#f0f0f0;line-height:1px;max-height:0px;max-width:0px;opacity:0;overflow:hidden;\">Physician-guided antiparasitic protocol, reviewed by a licensed provider and shipped discreetly.</div>\n<table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"background-color:#f0f0f0;\">\n<tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:32px 16px;\">\n<table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" style=\"max-width:600px;background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">\n<tr><td style=\"background:#0D1B2A;padding:20px 32px;border-bottom:3px solid #2bbcb3;\">\n  <table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr>\n    <td><img src=\"https://getclyrtoday.com/clyricon512.png\" alt=\"CLYR Health\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;border-radius:8px;\" /><span style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;vertical-align:middle;margin-left:12px;letter-spacing:0.5px;\">CLYR Health</span></td>\n    \n  </tr></table>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px 16px;\"><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:17px;line-height:1.6;color:#333333;text-align:left;\">Hi {{firstName}},</p></td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px 16px;\"><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:17px;line-height:1.6;color:#333333;text-align:left;\">You've trusted ivermectin before, so you already know the value of a clean, provider-guided protocol. We've made it simple to get one again, reviewed by a licensed provider and shipped straight to your door.</p></td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:0;text-align:center;\"><a href=\"https://www.clyr.health/antiparasitic.html?utm_source=cold_email&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=ivermectin_warm\"><img src=\"https://www.clyr.health/img/ivm-meb-protocol-email.jpg\" alt=\"Ivermectin plus Mebendazole antiparasitic protocol from $169 per month\" width=\"600\" style=\"display:block;width:100%;max-width:600px;height:auto;\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px 16px;\"><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:17px;line-height:1.6;color:#333333;text-align:left;\">Here's how it works: complete a short online intake, a licensed provider reviews your health profile, and your ivermectin plus mebendazole protocol ships discreetly from a state-licensed compounding pharmacy. <strong style=\"color:#1a1a2e;\">No waiting rooms, no contracts, cancel anytime.</strong></p></td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px 24px;\">\n  <table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"border:2px solid #2bbcb3;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;\">\n    <tr><td style=\"background:#0D1B2A;padding:12px;text-align:center;\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;color:#2bbcb3;text-transform:uppercase;\">Choose your protocol</span></td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:20px 16px;text-align:center;border-right:1px solid #eee;width:50%;background:#fafafa;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:10px;color:transparent;\">\u200e</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:6px 0 2px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a2e;\">Ivermectin</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:34px;font-weight:800;color:#1a1a2e;\">$139<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#999;font-weight:400;\">/mo</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:4px 0 0;font-size:11px;color:#888;\">or $369 for 3 months, save $48</p>\n    </td><td style=\"padding:20px 16px;text-align:center;width:50%;background:#fafafa;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:#fff;background:#2bbcb3;display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:8px;\">MOST POPULAR</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:6px 0 2px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a2e;\">Ivermectin + Mebendazole</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:34px;font-weight:800;color:#1a1a2e;\">$169<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#999;font-weight:400;\">/mo</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:4px 0 0;font-size:11px;color:#888;\">or $449 for 3 months, save $58</p>\n    </td></tr>\n  </table>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px 8px;\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://www.clyr.health/antiparasitic.html?utm_source=cold_email&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=ivermectin_warm\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#2bbcb3;color:#ffffff;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;padding:16px 48px;border-radius:10px;width:80%;text-align:center;\">Start Your Free Intake</a></td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"background:#f8f8f8;padding:20px 40px;border-top:1px solid #eee;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:11px;line-height:1.5;color:#aaaaaa;text-align:center;\">CLYR Health is a telehealth provider, not a pharmacy. Medications are compounded by state-licensed U.S. pharmacies and prescribed by licensed providers. Treatment is subject to provider approval and availability in most states. Compounded products are not FDA-approved.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#aaaaaa;text-align:center;\">Clyr Health, LLC \u00b7 <a href=\"https://www.clyr.health\" style=\"color:#2bbcb3;text-decoration:none;\">clyr.health</a> \u00b7 <a href=\"https://www.clyr.health/privacy.html\" style=\"color:#2bbcb3;text-decoration:none;\">Privacy</a> \u00b7 <a href=\"{{unsubscribe}}\" style=\"color:#aaaaaa;text-decoration:underline;\">Unsubscribe</a></p>\n</td></tr>\n</table></td></tr></table>\n</body></html>", "blocks": [{"id": "blk_header", "type": "header", "logoUrl": "https://getclyrtoday.com/clyricon512.png", "logoWidth": 36, "companyName": "CLYR Health", "showBadge": false, "badgeUrl": "", "bgColor": "#0D1B2A", "borderColor": "